data.description: Charming old Florida home located in Jensen Beach, 2 Bedroom / 1 Bath Single Family home with no HOA. Spanish tile throughout with an updated kitchen that overlooks the great room. Full Storm Protection Dade County approved shutters. Large Open Porch with huge yard providing extra space to park a boat or RV. Desirable location in Jensen Heights, minutes from the beach, boat launch, Riverside park. A+ schools. This pristine home is in a great location to Indian Riverside Park, Sailing Center, Dolphin Bar & Grill Restaurant. Minutes to downtown Jammin' Jensen. Close to beaches, Publix, shopping, Barbour's Produce stand. Jensen Beach noted for it's fine schools. Call today for an appointment!
